  "comment": "KUBE20BK Linkable Battery Uplight Outdoor: The KUBE20 is a linkable lightweight battery uplight equipped with a super bright 20W RGBWA-UV LED, ideal for use as accent and uplighting. The KUBE20 is designed for indoor and outdoor use and comes with an integrated battery that, when fully charged, lasts up to 12 hours depending on colour and intensity.  Communication is possible in a variety of ways, with IR, WIFI (App function) and wireless DMX. This makes the units easy to connect to each other. Delivery includes a multifunctional bracket, a magnetic filter package and two coupling pieces for easy connection of the KUBE fixtures.\n\n",
